info.author: Brian Rosner
info.description:
django-groups is a Django app that allows you to easily create "groups" of
people around arbitrary objects. For example, you might want a group of people
to collobrate on a wiki or tasks.

This app is extracted from the work that went into Pinax 0.7. It was written
to be extracted from the start.
